#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:eyewear_shop.homepage
msgid ""
"We are dedicated to providing you with the highest quality eye care and "
"expert guidance, every step of the way."
msgstr ""
"Vi gør os umage for at give dig den bedste øjenpleje og professionel "
"vejledning gennem hele forløbet."

#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:eyewear_shop.homepage
msgid "We create the perfect <br/>customized eye care plan for you"
msgstr "Vi tilpasser øjenplejen præcist<br/> til dine behov"

#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:eyewear_shop.homepage
msgid ""
"We offer a 30-day return policy for all products. Items must be in their "
"original condition, unused, and include the receipt or proof of purchase. "
"Refunds are processed within 5-7 business days of receiving the returned "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Vi tilbyder 30-dages returret på alle produkter. Varerne skal returneres i "
"deres originale emballage, være ubrugte og vedlægges kvittering eller "
"købsbevis. Refusioner behandles inden for 5–7 hverdage efter modtagelse af "
"den returnerede vare."

#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:eyewear_shop.homepage
msgid ""
"We’re committed to providing timely and effective eye care solutions to "
"ensure your satisfaction."
msgstr ""
"Vi arbejder målrettet på at levere hurtige og effektive øjenplejeløsninger, "
"så du får den bedst mulige oplevelse."

#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:eyewear_shop.homepage
msgid "What you will receive"
msgstr "Det får du"

#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:eyewear_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When making products available online, make sure you have enough stock. The "
"confirmation of a quotation or a website sale can triggers the creation of a "
"delivery order to your customer in the <strong>Inventory </strong>app. You "
"can\n"
"        always see how much of each product you have available in the "
"Inventory app menu, as well as on each individual product form."
msgstr ""
"Når du sælger produkter online, skal du sikre, at der er tilstrækkeligt "
"lager. Bekræftelse af et tilbud eller en onlineordre kan automatisk oprette "
"en leveringsordre til kunden i <strong>Lagerappen</strong>. Du kan\n"
"        altid se lagerbeholdningen for hvert produkt både i Lagerappens menu "
"og på den enkelte produktformular."

#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:eyewear_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller drøfte nogle spørgsmål mere "
"detaljeret?"

#. module: eyewear_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:eyewear_shop.homepage
msgid ""
"Write one or two paragraphs describing your product or services. To be "
"successful your content needs to be useful to your readers."
msgstr ""
"Skriv et eller to afsnit, der beskriver dit produkt eller dine ydelser. Dit "
"indhold har mest effekt, hvis det er nyttigt for dine læsere."

